<h4 id="architecture">Architecture</h4>
<p><img src="/images/AI-neural-network-design-rbf-network.png" /></p>

<h4 id="with-two-layer-perceptron-network">With Two Layer Perceptron Network</h4>
<ol>
  <li>In layer 1 of the RBF network, instead of performing an inner product
operation between the weights and input, we calculate the distance between
then input vector and the rows of the weight matrix.</li>
  <li>Second, instead of adding the bias, we multiply by the bias</li>
</ol>

